{
  "stem": "935.4",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And as we walked by him he said, my name is Max.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "My name is Max.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "Hurry, hurry.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "We are late.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "Hurry, hurry.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "We are late.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "And then it was pitch dark.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "We went into a wagon.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "We didn't know what that was either.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "Then we decided it was a van, because you could open the doors from the back.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "We could open the doors from the back.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "So we were in there, in that van.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "And they started driving.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "I have no idea.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "Pitch dark through Brussels.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "I mean, so fast, we were thrown about from-- and I knew that on both sides, there were little curtains and windows-- it was very strange-- and benches on the side.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "And we were looking for Red Cross uniforms, for doctor's uniforms, for nurse's [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "There was nothing there, nothing at all.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "And I don't know whether we drove 15 minutes, 20 minutes.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "I have no idea.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 45,
      "text": "And then, out of suddenly, the doors flew open, and we had lights much stronger than this here, and Germans, Germans, Germans.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 46,
      "text": "Raus, raus, raus, raus, raus.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 47,
      "text": "And we had driven right into Gestapo headquarters.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 48,
      "text": "Avenue-- Avenue Louise, famous Avenue Louise in Brussels.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 49,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And dear Max-- who, by the way, I hate to say this, is Jewish, was Jewish-- is the one who delivered us right into Gestapo headquarters.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 50,
      "text": "He was part of the whole scheme, this whole elaborate pyramid scheme.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I had sent cards, after I was in the little village, to my family.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Wonderful.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Everything is fine.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Come.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] As I had gotten from my friends, as they had gotten from their friends, and so forth, and so forth.",
      "word_count": 24
    }
  ],
